<h3 class="item__header"><a href="javascript:void(0)">The Simple Art of Murder</a></h3>

<div>
<p class="tertiary">The Simple Art of Murder refers to both a critical essay and a collection of short stories written by hard-boiled detective fiction author Raymond Chandler. The essay was first published in The Atlantic Monthly in December 1944. It was reprinted in 1950 along with eight of Chandler&#8217;s early stories pre-dating his first novel, The Big Sleep.</p>
